a.org/wiki/Ladislaus_Bortkiewicz" title=3D"Ladislaus Bortkiewicz">Ladislaus=
 Bortkiewicz</a> (1868=E2=80=931931),<sup id=3D"cite_ref-vonBortkiewitsch18=
98_12-1" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poiss=
on_distribution#cite_note-vonBortkiewitsch1898-12"><span class=3D"cite-brac=
ket">[</span>12<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup class=3D=
"reference nowrap"><span title=3D"Page: 23-25">:=E2=80=8A23-25=E2=80=8A</sp=
an></sup></li>
<li>yeast cells used when brewing <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/=
Guinness" title=3D"Guinness">Guinness</a> beer. This example was used by <a=
 href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Sealy_Gosset" title=3D"Willi=
am Sealy Gosset">William Sealy Gosset</a> (1876=E2=80=931937),<sup id=3D"ci=
te_ref-Student1907_62-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedi=
a.org/wiki/Poisson_distribution#cite_note-Student1907-62"><span class=3D"ci=
te-bracket">[</span>62<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup i=
d=3D"cite_ref-Boland1984_63-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wi=
kipedia.org/wiki/Poisson_distribution#cite_note-Boland1984-63"><span class=
=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>63<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>=
</li>
<li>phone calls arriving at a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Call=
_centre" title=3D"Call centre">call centre</a> within a minute. This exampl=
e was described by <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agner_Krarup_Er=
lang" title=3D"Agner Krarup Erlang">A.K. Erlang</a> (1878=E2=80=931929),<su=
p id=3D"cite_ref-Erlang1909_64-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en=
.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson_distribution#cite_note-Erlang1909-64"><span cla=
ss=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>64<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></su=
p></li>
<li>goals in sports involving two competing teams,<sup id=3D"cite_ref-Hornb=
y2014_65-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Po=
isson_distribution#cite_note-Hornby2014-65"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[<=
/span>65<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>deaths per year in a given age group,<sup id=3D"cite_ref-66" class=3D"r=
eference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson_distribution#cit=
e_note-66"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>66<span class=3D"cite-brack=
et">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>jumps in a stock price in a given time interval,</li>
<li>times a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_server" title=3D"W=
eb server">web server</a> is accessed per minute (under an assumption of <a=
 href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson_process#Homogeneous" class=
