<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mutation" title=3D"Mutation">m=
utations</a> in a given stretch of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki=
/DNA" title=3D"DNA">DNA</a> after a certain amount of radiation,</li>
<li><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cells_(biology)" class=3D"mw-r=
edirect" title=3D"Cells (biology)">cells</a> infected at a given <a href=3D=
"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multiplicity_of_infection" title=3D"Multipli=
