<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Other_applications_in_scien=
ce">Other applications in science</h3></div>
<p>In a Poisson process, the number of observed occurrences fluctuates abou=
t its mean <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">=CE=BB=
</span> with a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standard_deviation"=
 title=3D"Standard deviation">standard deviation</a> <span class=3D"mwe-mat=
h-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mw=
e-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.o=
rg/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle \sigma _{k}=3D{\sqrt {\lambd=
